Class SalesRecord

java.lang.Object
SalesRecord
class SalesRecord
extends java.lang.Object
SaleRecord is an object that holds an array of Sale objects and contains a value for number of sales in the array. Its methods are based on ordering and maintenance of the array.
Author:
rshum
